{"tid":2448864,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"運輸署車輛檢驗綜合大樓四月一日起分階段啓用","createTime":"2021-03-16T08:30:45.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-18T21:45:49.000Z","uid":244704,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"33ebf941ae5f2ad3ce3ef2b2c52d8de986a29ac9","tid":2448864,"uid":244704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T08:30:45.000Z","msg":"　　運輸署今日（三月十六日）表示，全新落成的多層運輸署車輛檢驗綜合大樓（驗車大樓）由四月一日起分階段啓用，以重置三個現有政府驗車中心，即新九龍灣驗車中心、九龍灣驗車中心及土瓜灣驗車中心。該三個驗車中心將於重置後停止運作。<br />\n<br />\n階段：第一階段<br />\n日期：二○二一年四月一日<br />\n驗車大樓啓用樓層：地下<br />\n重置的現有驗車中心：新九龍灣驗車中心<br />\n<br />\n階段：第二階段<br />\n日期：二○二一年第二季<br />\n驗車大樓啓用樓層： 一樓<br />\n重置的現有驗車中心：九龍灣驗車中心<br />\n<br />\n階段：第三階段<br />\n日期：二○二一年第二季<br />\n驗車大樓啓用樓層：二樓<br />\n重置的現有驗車中心：土瓜灣驗車中心<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202103/16/P2021031600324.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F202103%2F16%2FP2021031600324.htm&d=HziU8jWK8j2Oa3ZLfTDirPhh9XvCW3eHRhDz%2B7Q%2FvTo%3D&h=2be9cdfa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202103/16/P2021031600324.htm</a>"},{"pid":"080d374970b45385d8f2b3d0b165b9c23c2acf03","tid":2448864,"uid":126961,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T08:50:44.000Z","msg":"有咩用 平時都唔係去依啲地方驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e1af245e6d7b2114d10064653d9524ef92fed61","tid":2448864,"uid":208952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"080d374970b45385d8f2b3d0b165b9c23c2acf03","tid":2448864,"uid":126961,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T08:50:44.000Z","msg":"有咩用 平時都唔係去依啲地方驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T09:36:24.000Z","msg":"商用車用"},{"pid":"941cb85b6c93b5c0e54122e18cf1cf7612cecfff","tid":2448864,"uid":33868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T09:37:26.000Z","msg":"拎咗架車去驗，唔知去邊好<br />\n分